#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Problems</h2>
This page collects issues with %%PRODUCT%% that may or may not get fixed.
<ol>
    <li>The system has evolved and there are obsolete and unused pieces of it which need to be actively
        removed, particularly that software which is not likely to work anyways.  For instance:
	<ol>
	    <li>You used to be able to e-mail route results back if the e-mail was in EXACTLY
	        the right format.  That was not only difficult to do, but using web forms
		was always going to be easier.  All of the code associated with that should
		be removed and the rest simplified where possible.</li>
	</ol></li>
    <li>You cannot hand a random person a route sheet and create a new driver after the route is
	complete.</li>
    <li>The concept of "Administrator" needs to be flushed out and enforced.</li>
    <li>Form input it trusted far more than it should be.</li>
</ol>
